ort" UTC="true">20110809T06:00:00</Date><Author type="string" label="Author's Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">missing value</Author><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[<h1>Chinese Opera Orchestra&nbsp;&nbsp; of Shanghai</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Tuesday, September 20, 7:30 P.M.</h2>
<h2>Barrus Concert Hall</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The founding of the Chinese Opera Orchestra of Shanghai in 2010 was heralded as a major event in preserving and popularizing Chinese traditional music and in making it accessible to people throughout the world. &nbsp;The orchestra specializes in bringing richly crafted arrangements of Chinese folk music and exciting performances of the best music from the repertoire of traditional Chinese opera. &nbsp;The musicians play many traditional Chinese instruments, including the erhu, guzheng, pipa, sanxian, suona, liuqin, sheng, paixiao, yangqin, zhongyuan, zhongyuan, jinghu, dizi, zhonghu, konghou, and gaohu. &nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>RATING: TRADITIONAL CHINESE MUSIC</p>
<p><em>Tickets go on sale August 29. &nbsp;Cost is $12 for general public, $6 for BYU-Idaho students. &nbsp;No children under 6. &nbsp;Event dress. &nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/Tickets/" title="Ticket Office" target="_parent">Click here to order tickets.</a></em></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="News" label="News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="NewsNavigationComponent"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Name="xPower" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes=""/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false" Navigation="Ancestors" GenerationOrder="down" StartPage="x5" MaxNodes="" MaxDepth="" Query=""/><xPower Type="Component" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Component="x18179" CompTypes="SiteControl"/></NewsDetail>
